---
import { navigationLinks, socialLinks } from '../utils/content'

const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<footer
  id="footer"
  class="w-full space-y-6 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10 text-center text-xs text-slate-500 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 md:text-sm"
>
  <nav aria-label="Navegación inferior" class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm font-medium">
    {navigationLinks.map((link) => (
      <a
        href={`/#${link.id}`}
        class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-600 transition hover:bg-[#0CA000]/15 hover:text-[#0CA000] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#06C300] dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-[#06C300]/15 dark:hover:text-[#06C300]"
      >
        {link.name}
      </a>
    ))}
  </nav>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
    {socialLinks.map((link) => (
      <a
        href={link.href}
        target={link.href.startsWith('http') ? '_blank' : undefined}
        rel={link.href.startsWith('http') ? 'noopener noreferrer' : undefined}
        class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transition hover:border-[#0CA000] hover:text-[#0CA000] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-[#06C300] dark:border-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:border-[#06C300] dark:hover:text-[#06C300]"
      >
        <img src={link.icon} alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="h-5 w-5" />
        <span class="sr-only">{link.label}</span>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
    “Todo gran desarrollador llegó ahí resolviendo problemas para los que no estaba preparado... hasta que lo estuvo.” — Patrick
    McKenzie
  </p>
  <p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">© {year} Thiago Martins. Creado con Astro & Tailwind CSS.</p>
</footer>
